		<div class="ornament-divider" aria-hidden="true">&#8212;</div>
		<p class="meta" style="margin:0; font-style: italic;">
			&copy; {today.getFullYear()} Alfarrabios do Adi.
		</p>
		<p class="meta" style="margin: var(--space-sm) 0 0 0;">
			<a href="/rss.xml">RSS</a> &middot;
			<a href="https://github.com/adibaldo/adibaldo.github.io" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">GitHub</a>
		</p>
		<p class="meta" style="margin: var(--space-md) 0 0 0;">
			Se achou um erro, me avise com calma.
		</p>
	</div>
</footer>
